data.name: lblAddingACustomControl.Text
data.value: Only Custom counters can be incremented or decremented. You must first create a Custom Performance Counter manually. To do this, open the "Server Explorer" in Visual Studio .NET, open up Servers -> your computer name -> Performance Counters. Right click "Performance Counters" and click "Create New Category". Create a category and a new counter. Press "Refresh" to reload the categories in this form.
